<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=120 BGCOLOR="#DDDDDD"><FONT CLASS=GraphicCaption>"Hey there groovemeisters!  Welcome to Firona's Loooove Shack.  I'm your main lounge lizard, and we'll be playing all the hits, starting with Saturday Night Fever."</FONT></TD>
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><IMG SRC="images/spacer.gif"></TD>
